{"tid":757131,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知呢隻係咩昆蟲？","createTime":"2018-07-26T14:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T00:57:22.000Z","uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de9f6974c0c356a935f1c0ad390d63a6a2492887","tid":757131,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T14:31:32.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴 圖係下面 影得好細粒<br />\n<br />\n事源係我砌左張松木書枱，冇搽光油嘅<br />\n<br />\n想問有冇人知呢隻係咩黎？ 因為每日起碼會有一兩隻係我玩緊電腦嘅時間爬出黎，好困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會唔會係&lsquo;&rsquo;塞&lsquo;&rsquo;黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/222729_a238c41b66ff597b9d9b7532628cbd3a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F222729_a238c41b66ff597b9d9b7532628cbd3a.png&h=8e9e8c34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14e6cd642ba5d45e0fa04f73ae4222b3cd50b1b6","tid":757131,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1252454d5d17e17fa61f6017c3cbcea8ac212c07","tid":757131,"uid":129658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:59:02.000Z","msg":"下世小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff045ec709ee1b371e14a3e3e2e6e7220f8478b","tid":757131,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"西野巴蟲"},{"pid":"4ab667014c16e5481d0534f8343cfb42782cf5ff","tid":757131,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:57:22.000Z","msg":"認真啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}